## Additional Terms for Educational Use

This software is specifically designed to provide free AI education to
underprivileged learners worldwide. While the MIT license allows commercial
use, we encourage organizations using this software to:

1. Keep educational services free or low-cost for underprivileged students
2. Contribute improvements back to the community
3. Maintain accessibility standards
4. Respect student privacy and data protection
5. Share success stories to inspire others

